{"tid":2186910,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"[SellHK] Wetland Seasons Park 3期上樓書　面積由291呎起","createTime":"2020-09-03T09:43:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T09:49:28.000Z","uid":75355,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cbff0c9e93905a259ee7b7e601ff9b8cbe9c5329","tid":2186910,"uid":75355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T09:43:58.000Z","msg":"淡友戰好友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wetlandseasonspark3.com.hk/#tc/brochure\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wetlandseasonspark3.com.hk%2F%23tc%2Fbrochure&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hZq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=dd485040\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wetlandseasonspark3.com.hk/#tc/brochure</a><br />\n<br />\nSellHK（0016）旗下天水圍第3期Wetland Seasons Park剛上載樓書，涉及318個單位，實用面積由291至816方呎，市場估計，最快於下周公布價單。<br />\n<br />\nWetland Seasons Park 3期分佈於1座、7座、8座及9座，當中一房戶間隔佔15%；兩房單位佔51%；三房單位則佔34%。其官方網頁在前日（9月1日）正式啟用，約80%的單位為標準分層，共設有九種戶型，餘下為特色單位。<br />\n<br />\n據樓書，面積最細的單位為9座地下A3室，實用面積291方呎，設有97方呎花園。面積最大的單位為1座5樓A1室，實用面積816方呎。"},{"pid":"cb8e1b65ec9c2a12955503c39f5626ea05e47f71","tid":2186910,"uid":239912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T09:49:28.000Z","msg":"呢度有位淡友 終於可以再去抽喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前2輪都抽唔到 好嬲好介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}